Importance Score: 80/100

## Team Joining Process
- Dual joining methods:
  1. Direct team code entry
  2. Team search functionality with name/captain filtering
- Membership validation rules:
  - Team size limits
  - Sport-specific roster requirements
  - Division-based eligibility checks
Importance Score: 75/100

